gagement, and social media influencer marketing and advertising services. It also provides web development services, including e-commerce sites, content management systems, PHP websites, customized web development, custom AI solutions, and script-based web project services; web design services, including PSD to HTML/WordPress/Magento, UI/UX design, mobile responsive web designs, website landing page development, custom website design, and mockup to final website services; and website maintenance services comprising website content/image updates, website technical upgrades, WordPress and plugin updates, website hosting and security, and regular site backups services. In addition, the company offers app development services for Android consisting of m-commerce, social media, GPS-based, mobile games, and custom apps, as well as widget development; app development services for IOS, including iPod/iPad, social, education, travel, and banking applications, as well as back-end support; content creation services, such as review, blog, press release, website copy, and infographic content writing; and outsourcing services. Further, it provides domain registration, SaaS platforms, advanced web programming, server management, open-source customization, web and mobile application, digital media, social media optimization, pay per click, and payment gateway integration services. The company exports its products and services. Megri Soft Limited was incorporated in 1992 and is headquartered in Chandigarh, India."}}